Vegas("Country Pop").
  withData(
    Seq(
      Map("country" -> "CH", "population" -> 1379),
      Map("country" -> "USA", "population" -> 323),
      Map("country" -> "UK", "population" -> 65),
      Map("country" -> "IT", "population" -> 60)
    )
  ).
  encodeX("country", Nom).
  encodeY("population", Quant).
  mark(Bar).
  show
